<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Error - MongoDB Learning App</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/common.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .error-container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    .error-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      color: #dc3545;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .error-code {
      font-size: 6rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #667eea;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle error-icon"></i>
    
    <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined') { %>
      <h1 class="error-code">Error</h1>
      <h2 class="text-dark mb-3"><%= error %></h2>
      
      <% if (typeof details !== 'undefined') { %>
        <div class="alert alert-danger">
          <strong>Detalles:</strong> <%= details %>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    <% } else { %>
      <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
      <h2 class="text-dark mb-3">Página No Encontrada</h2>
    <% } %>
    
    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
      Lo sentimos, algo salió mal. La página que buscas no está disponible o ha ocurrido un error.
    </p>
    
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Ir al Inicio
      </a>
      <a href="/mapa" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
        <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt me-2"></i>Ver Mapa
      </a>
      <a href="/catalogo" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart me-2"></i>Ver Catálogo
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <hr class="my-4">
    
    <div class="text-muted">
      <small>
        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-1"></i>
        MongoDB Learning App - Proyecto Educativo
      </small>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>